  "text": "Hradis et al. [CITATION_1] proposes an FCN-based deblurring method. The core FCN maps the input image which is blurred and generates a deblurred image. They collect a dataset of well-taken images of documents, and process them with kernels designed to mimic hand-shake and defocus.",
